name: Crystal of Xandar - Galactible Genesis
description: HUZZAH!!! You've discovered the Crystal of Xandar! This is the first of 99 "Galactibles" made by Pyramid Guy, aka Kris Kanaly. Collect Galactibles to raise your Mana as you traverse the Galactiverse!! Each Galactible is a one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles drop every week on twitter, so give us a follow. Certified authentic, original animations. Music by Sawsquarenoise!  Galactibles Â©2021
